            "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p><hr /><p>One of your personal trinkets has aged from years of love and wear. Looking at it reminds you of times when you were safe and filled with joy, such as when you were a child listening to stories of heroic triumph. When you use the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Self Soothe] action, you also reduce your @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Doomed] value by 1. You cannot use this to reduce a permanent doomed value.</p>"
